title: Cabin for work machine

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a cabin for work machine, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front view of the cabin for work machine showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a rear view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a reduced left side view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a reduced right side view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a reduced top plan view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a reduced right front perspective view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a reduced left rear perspective view thereof; and,
FIG. 8 is a reduced right side view showing the cabin in use condition.
The broken line showing of the work machine in FIG. 8 is included for the purpose of illustrating environment only and forms no part of the claimed design.
